Package com.macys.azure.jms.relay

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMessageRelay
    This interface defines constant values used in this package and message relay functionality.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseRelayer
    This is the abstract base class for the several concrete Relayer classes.
    EventHubRelayer
    Instances of this class relay a message to Azure EventHub.
    RocketMQToAPIRepayer
    This is class implements a source and sink model, where this class will be running as the Scalable pipe (broker) between the message source and destination The message source will be RocketMQ at Alibaba JST The destination will be the Azure Service Bus abstract behind the reset API
    ServiceBusRelayer
    Instances of this class relay a message to Azure ServiceBus.
    StorageBlobRelayer
    Instances of this class relay a message to an Azure Storage Blob.
    StorageQueueRelayer
    Instances of this class relay a message to an Azure Storage Queue.
